<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>DAIHNAK CAAH A TLING CANG CH128</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Misual mi nih thachin bia, An hngal kho hlei lo; Jesuh a thi nangmah
 ca, A chim a rau cang,

[C1]
   Daihnak ca ah a tling cang, Tuahser awk vialte, A sualmi khamhnak ca
   ah, Tuahnak a tling cang.

[V2]
 Vancung in Jesuh a tum, Lei ah a thi cang, Harnak vialte a tei dih, A
 bia ngai tuah u,

[C2]
   Daihnak ca ah a tling cang, Tuahser awk vialte, A sualmi khamhnak ca
   ah, Tuahnak a tling cang.

[V3]
 A thami kha kawl awkah, Nan zuam cio cang maw? Kan duh kawlnak dih
 cang seh, Van in a pen cang,

[C3]
   Daihnak ca ah a tling cang, Tuahser awk vialte, A sualmi khamhnak ca
   ah, Tuahnak a tling cang.

[V4]
 Bawi Jesuh bia va zum law, A min bochan tuah, Mit-hmai tha nih an hloh
 khawh, Pamnak a kan pek.

[C4]
   Daihnak ca ah a tling cang, Tuahser awk vialte, A sualmi khamhnak ca
   ah, Tuahnak a tling cang.

[V5]
 Mit-hmai tha na kawlmi kha, Vawlei ah chia ta, Bawipa he na um ahcun,
 Na tei khawh cang lai.

[C5]
   Daihnak ca ah a tling cang, Tuahser awk vialte, A sualmi khamhnak ca
   ah, Tuahnak a tling cang.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>128</hymn_number>
</song>